      "content": "Gower Street station. The platform has a different quality to Baker Street: younger passengers, men carrying instrument cases, the particular restlessness of people who spend their days thinking.\n\nUCL is five minutes north. The medical school is across the road. This is the station of people who work with their minds, which Ida finds both interesting and alienating in roughly equal measure."
    },
