      "content": "Gower Street. Wide, institutional, lined with buildings that mean to be taken seriously. A medical practice occupies a Georgian terrace across from the station exit. A pharmacy at street level, consulting rooms above. A brass plate on the door: *Dr. E. Voss, M.D.*"
    },
