          "0.2"
        ]
      ],
      "content": "A consulting room above the pharmacy. Clean, spare, the smell of carbolic and something underneath it that is harder to name. A desk with a leather top, papers arranged with professional exactness. Two filing cabinets against the wall, both locked.\n\nDr. Voss receives patients on Mondays, Wednesdays, and Fridays. On other days the room is sometimes occupied by a different kind of business."
    },
    {
      "kind": 30078,
