      "content": "The courtyard of University College London. Students cross at speed, carrying books, arguing in pairs. Nobody asks Ida what she is doing here \u2014 there are enough people moving through that one more is invisible.\n\nThis is the most educated place she has ever stood. She is aware of this the way you are aware of cold \u2014 not unpleasantly, but as a fact about the world."
    },
    {
      "kind": 30078,
      "tags": [
