          "ambient",
          "0.4"
        ]
      ],
      "content": "Streets between Gower Street and Portland Road. Not quite either neighbourhood, carrying the slightly provisional quality of areas that have not yet decided what they are. Lodging houses, a few respectable terraces, a pub on the corner.\n\nIda has begun to know this part of London the way she knows Saffron Hill \u2014 not as home, but as territory."
    },
