          "complete"
        ]
      ],
      "content": "A man in his fifties with a careful, unhurried manner. His practice is legitimate \u2014 he treats patients, keeps proper records, has a good reputation in the neighbourhood.\n\nHe also does other things. He has told himself for years that the other things are a small part of his work. He has been telling himself this for long enough that he is no longer certain it is true."
    },
