          "30078:<PUBKEY>:metropolitan:quest:quill-job-4",
          "complete"
        ]
      ],
      "content": "A woman of about forty, plainly dressed in a way that suggests choice rather than constraint. She has the stillness of someone always listening to more than the current conversation.\n\nShe gives Ida no name. Ida does not ask for one. They understand each other in the specific way of people who operate in the same world without having chosen to be in it together."
    },
    {
      "kind": 30078,
      "tags": [
