        ]
      ],
      "content": "A young man of about twenty, ink on his hands, carrying more books than he can comfortably manage. He has the slightly stunned quality of someone in their first year of serious study.\n\nHe dropped his notebook somewhere between the library and the courtyard. He has not yet noticed."
    },
