      "content": "A woman who receives the package at Baker Street and carries it west to Edgware Road. The exchange at the platform column looks like nothing. She is entirely ordinary.\n\nShe is the second hand."
    },
    {
      "kind": 30078,
      "tags": [
        [
          "d",
