      "content": "A student's field notebook, densely written. Pages of geological observation from the Metropolitan Railway dig \u2014 soil strata, depth records, structural notes.\n\nNear the back: a sketch of an unexplained chamber encountered near King's Cross during the 1860 dig. Annotated: *sealed on instruction, not recorded in survey log. reason not given.*\n\nThe student does not know what this means. Ida is beginning to."
    },
    {
      "kind": 30078,
      "tags": [
