        ]
      ],
      "content": "The spine uncracked. No one has opened it since it was shelved.\n\nThe preliminary survey for the Metropolitan Railway, 1860. The findings are listed methodically \u2014 until a gap, three pages sealed together with a paper band. Someone bound these pages shut after the report was written.\n\nOn the outside of the band, in pencil: *See supplementary record. Restricted.*\n\nThere is no supplementary record on this shelf."
    },
    {
      "kind": 30078,
      "tags": [
