          ""
        ]
      ],
      "content": "Six folders. She opens the first: a medical assessment in Voss's handwriting \u2014 careful, clinical, concluding the patient is in full possession of their faculties. Clipped to it, the Quill's version of the same assessment. Different conclusion, different signature.\n\nHarwick.\n\nAll six folders. The same signature on every Quill document. The same name from the green ledger.\n\nShe puts the folders back exactly as she found them. She locks the drawer. She hands Voss the key.\n\nShe does not tell him what she found. He already knows."
    },
